body:
@agriasgg Thanks! But if that's truly the case, then that should be included as a note, imo. I was under the assumption that the model was _only_ looking at the same CSV data every time, which means it should have arrived to `[1,2]` every time. 

Nowhere in the example documentation did it say that every run was going to affect the subsequent outputs.
